cope and reported here. The catalog\nincludes 54 of the 65 CHVCs listed by Braun and Burton (1999) on the basis of a\nvisual search of the LDS data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2002 16:50:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
